entries.precis: Mostly cloudy. Medium (50%) chance of showers. Light winds becoming east to northeasterly 15 to 25 km/h in the middle of the day.
Cloudy. High (70%) chance of showers in the morning and afternoon. Winds northeasterly 15 to 25 km/h turning northerly 15 to 20 km/h in the evening.
Mostly sunny day. Medium (50%) chance of showers in the evening. The chance of a thunderstorm in the evening. Light winds becoming northerly 15 to 25 km/h during the morning.
Slight (30%) chance of a shower or thunderstorm during the morning. Sunny afternoon. Winds northwesterly 15 to 25 km/h tending west to northwesterly 15 to 20 km/h during the afternoon.
Sunny. Light winds becoming westerly 15 to 20 km/h during the day.
Sunny. Light winds becoming westerly 15 to 25 km/h during the morning.
